    OBus_match_rule_lexer,
    OBus_protocol,
    OBus_type_ext_lexer,
    OBus_util,
    OBus_xml_parser,
    OBus_config
  BuildDepends: lwt.unix, lwt_react, lwt.syntax, lwt.syntax.log, type_conv, xmlm
  XMETARequires: lwt.unix, lwt_react, xmlm
  XMETADescription: Pure OCaml implementation of D-Bus

